node.text:
These are are ball bearing slides.
.
Getting the most out of the space in our kitchens and homes is aided by adding pull out shelves. These products help organize your storage and can even have power outlets added for charging your phones, tablets and more.
.
@regencydesignandbuild
.
Slides for slide out shelving or drawers are made different to offer both smoother operation or to help keep options affordable. They are made as either ball bearing slides or roller slides.
.
For the best in pull out shelf slides ball bearings give the best and smoothest motion. This keeps all of your pots and pans stacked the way you leave them. Another benefit of ball bearing slides is they offer full extension. This means you can get the shelves all the way out to reach the very back.
.
Roller slides are a great budget option. These slides help extend shelves to get to most of the items, and make a reach much shorter to reach the back. They come out about 75% of the full length of the shelf.
.
There are many advantages and benefits of having pull out shelves. They make life in your kitchen and bathrooms easier and much more organized. Everything will have a place, and will be easy to get out when you need it and just as easy to put back when you are done.
.
.
Norm 
@regencydesignandbuild
.
.
.
